Metadata.Title: Fall of The Carlisle Empire for Good
Metadata.Description: A contract has been issued, and you have been cleared to engage. Eliminate every target as clean and as quiet as possible, Destroy every vehicle so that no one can escape the manor and get police and (Optional->) if you can at the end Subdue or Eliminate remaining Carlisle Family Members and hide their bodies.We need to stop the Carlisle Empire from SPREADING!!!
